text: Calliotropis cynee is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Eucyclidae. ==Description== The length of the shell reaches 17 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Indonesia. ==References== * Vilvens C. (2007) New records and new species of Calliotropis from Indo- Pacific. Novapex 8 (Hors Série 5): 1–72 ==External links== * cynee Category:Gastropods described in 2007
title: Calliotropis cynee
